      <title>巴西不断扩大的财政赤字给预算目标带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/brazil-s-widening-fiscal-deficit-piles-pressure-on-budget-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中央政府收入下降，巴西 11 月份的财政赤字较上年扩大，凸显了总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 在寻求 2024 年支撑公共账户时面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/brazil-s-widening-fiscal-deficit-piles-pressure-on-budget-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:55:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚议员称对大亨丹格特的突袭将损害经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nigerian-lawmaker-says-raid-on-tycoon-dangote-will-hurt-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚议会一个有影响力的小组主席表示，尼日利亚反腐败官员对亿万富翁阿里科·丹格特控制的丹格特工业有限公司的办公室进行突击搜查，将损害经济并吓退投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/nigerian-lawmaker-says-raid-on-tycoon-dangote-will-hurt-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:26:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的教育主管敦促对学生贷款债务减免保持耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/cardona-says-officials-aim-to-fix-broken-student-loan-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[教育部长米格尔·卡多纳敦促政府在政府处理学生贷款债务减免的后续步骤时保持耐心，这是总统乔·拜登的一项标志性举措，他表示官员们正在处理一个已损坏的系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/cardona-says-officials-aim-to-fix-broken-student-loan-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:24:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登预算负责人对美国能否避免停摆并不乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-budget-director-not-optimistic-congress-can-avoid-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的最高预算官员表示，她担心美国政府本月将部分关闭，因为国会和白宫在边境安全和支出水平方面陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-budget-director-not-optimistic-congress-can-avoid-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油资源丰富的索马里邦特兰地区在紧张局势中选举领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/oil-rich-puntland-region-of-somalia-elects-leader-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[邦特兰是索马里东部石油资源丰富的半自治领土，将于 1 月 8 日在议会投票中选出新总统，此时摩加迪沙正忙着试图控制索马里兰的分裂地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/oil-rich-puntland-region-of-somalia-elects-leader-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 14:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州率先获得从加拿大进口更便宜药品的批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-fda-approves-florida-plan-to-import-drugs-from-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府将允许佛罗里达州从加拿大进口更便宜的处方药，为该州几年前启动的一项计划开了绿灯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-fda-approves-florida-plan-to-import-drugs-from-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 14:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院陷入僵局，议长约翰逊考虑与拜登就边境问题进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/speaker-weighs-talks-with-biden-on-border-as-senate-stalls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，众议院议长迈克·约翰逊正在考虑寻求与总统乔·拜登就乌克兰援助和边境政策进行直接会谈，因为两党妥协的谈判在参议院陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/speaker-weighs-talks-with-biden-on-border-as-senate-stalls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 14:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因反对派赢得伊斯坦布尔的埃尔多安竞争对手寻求新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/turkey-local-elections-istanbul-opposition-mayor-imamoglu-runs-for-new-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯坦布尔市长埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁是土耳其最大反对党的关键人物，被广泛认为是总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的潜在挑战者，他将在 3 月 31 日的地方选举中竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/turkey-local-elections-istanbul-opposition-mayor-imamoglu-runs-for-new-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的白宫竞选贯穿法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-2024-campaign-starts-in-iowa-runs-through-courtrooms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在爱荷华州，前总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 似乎有望在 1 月 15 日举行的全国首次预选会议上获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-2024-campaign-starts-in-iowa-runs-through-courtrooms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非运动员奥斯卡·皮斯托利斯假释出狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-05/south-african-athlete-oscar-pistorius-to-be-released-on-parole-after-nearly-9-years-in-prison</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非比勒陀利亚（美联社）——奥运会短跑运动员奥斯卡·皮斯托利斯 (Oscar Pistorius) 是一位双截肢者，他在骑着碳纤维刀片跑步时成为了这项运动最高水平的全球明星。他因杀害女友模特瑞娃·斯汀坎普 (Reeva Steenkamp) 服刑近九年，于周五出狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-05/south-african-athlete-oscar-pistorius-to-be-released-on-parole-after-nearly-9-years-in-prison</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 05:59:04 GMT</pubDate>
